# Master Control Orchestration Server - line-ending policy.
#
# The repository's canonical text encoding is LF. Windows checkouts with
# core.autocrlf=true otherwise smudge the working tree to CRLF, which
# breaks Test-MCOSMarkdownLinks.ps1 (its fence-blanking regex anchors on
# LF-only line ends) and invalidates protected-path SHA-256 comparisons
# against the handoff hash tables.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Binary payloads - never subject to EOL conversion.
*.png binary
*.ico binary
*.bmp binary
*.rtf binary
